Asstant
=======

Asstant is a Discord bot that answers questions using OpenAI.

Requirements
------------

* Node
* [A Discord App](https://discord.com/developers/docs/getting-started#creating-an-app)
* [An Open AI API key](https://platform.openai.com/account/api-keys)

Usage
-----

On your server computer:

1. Download dependencies: `npm install`.

2. Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and edit it to have the right credentials for
Discord and OpenAI.

3. (One time) register the bot commands in your Discord app: `node asstant.mjs deploy`.

4. Start the bot: `npm asstant.mjs start`.

In your Discord server:

`/question What is love?`
